Package: MuniCandS
Type: Package
Title: Multivariate Tests of Uniformity, Normality, Symmetry and Independence
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(person("Alejandra", "Cabana", email = "AnaAlejandra.Cabana@uab.cat", role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Enrique M.", "Cabana", role = "aut"))
Description: Implements multivariate tests of uniformity on the hypercube and hypersphere, as well as tests of normality, spherical symmetry, elliptical symmetry and independence. The procedures are of Cramér-von Mises type and are based on a decomposition of the empirical process into asymptotically independent components.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
